reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very high quality for the price.
reviews.reviewText: What I like the most is there is no visible white diffuser which is a huge deal in an all black build. The quality is incredible for the price. Most impressive is the cables come with a braided sleeve which classes up the install even more. The color is great. The only thi g I would like to se added is light on both sides of the fan. The lights are only on the intake side. I have ordered them several different times for different build due to the high quality and great performance the 5 pack comes with a controller hub also.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Fans! Work great and Recommend!
reviews.reviewText: I love these fans. They work great and color is awesome. I would recommend others to buy them. The ONLY complaint I would have is that the color is only on one side. So in my case, in order to get the proper air flow, some of the fans are facing the wrong way to see the lights. That is kind of disappointing, but not enough for me to stop using them. As long as you are ok with that, then they are great. I can't speak on how long the fans will last since I just installed them, but they are working great so far. The pricing was great as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great fans for the money
reviews.reviewText: These are very nice fans for the price i got it for, it does get loud if u are running fan on max but you can change that in your mobo software and set a curvev when the fan kicks in, my fans are very quiet because my rig dont run super hot, it rarely runs above 70 degree so my fan never needs to run in max.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These fans look great the RGB makes it simple to add to your motherboard. The fans are smooth and heavy duty, and provide ample amount of air pressure.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great fans and rgb
reviews.reviewText: Bought it for my cousin and she loved it great looks and really quiet fans

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 13, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice and quiet fans with a controller that will work on 3rd party fans too.
reviews.reviewText: I ended up getting a 5 pack of these, then a single, and then a pair of the 140mm fans too. I have dual fan 120mm coolers that are from another company as well, The 5 pack of the 120mm fans and the 2 pack of the 140mm fans came with controllers, and since I am using a server mobo, a Machinist X99 D8-Max, that was needed since I do not have an RGB controller of any type on it.The fans are very nice and quiet. The controllers are easy to connect and mount. As far as power for the fans themselves you do not need to hook them to the controller, just hook them in as normal with CPU fans to the proper place and the rest of the fans to wherever provides the proper 12 volt power and has the connections needed, otherwise they will run full speed.With the controllers you can also hook in ARGB fans that are from another company. I have 3 of the 120mm fans and both of the 140mm fans hooked into one controller, the other 3 120mm fans and the dual fan CPU coolers ran into a splitter on each and back to the other spots on the other controller. All of the fans are connected to the motherboard itself for the actual fan power.To get to different patterns with the fans you will click on a button on the controller so make sure you have things set to where you can get to them to change settings. There aren't a whole lot of different ones, but there are enough patterns to make things look really cool. I went for the one that goes through all of the colors, but didn't quite get them synched up. You honestly aren't going to beat the quality, airflow, and quietness of these fans for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great built quality!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I was looking for fans with halos to go along with my Corsair AIO. Unfortunately Corsair at this moment doesn't have fans that are appealing to me. I purchased these and they are exactly what I was looking for. They are bright, fairly quiet, they cool just the same as my Corsair fans, and go perfect with a black case like mine.I also purchased an adapter so I could plug them into the Commander Pro and now I can control them through iCue which in my opinion is the best RGB software. I have a Gigabyte mobo and RGB Fusion is garbage for controlling RGB, one simple adapter solves that issue.I am 100% satisfied with these fans.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Nice Quiet fans with oomph
reviews.reviewText: These are great fans but these companies do RGB as an after thought then advertise is as a feature. the controller will not hold its program. Set it then set it again on next reboot be prepared to do it yet again.bad experience.
